3:15:19.000Z","msg":"應該同第一個放干擾器玩鳩考生個人心態一樣"},{"pid":"209561ee29bb03be123972cfcd0b40bd00525a31","tid":1285153,"uid":246764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9936f3bf5e9054af81f1a0bd893dd3b21c544f6d","tid":1285153,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:51:47.000Z","msg":"咁負碌食法都比佢諗到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:22:38.000Z","msg":"其實當年係迫不得已先用芥末汁架，咁啱又咁合又真係抵死。<br />\n段故係咁嘅，話說1950年代咁街邊興起小販吖賣下魚旦車仔麵牛雜咁嘅，提供嘅醬汁都係豉油吖、花生醬、茄汁吖或者係茄汁加辣汁調和嘅醬咁。<br />\n咁點解會岀現芥末汁呢，係因為當年華人同老外有場爭議係關於茄汁，點解茄汁英文係ketchup而唔係tomato sauce呢就係因為當年茄汁在華銷售極大，華人就正名茄汁叫ketchup，但外國商人就唔順從，發起禁售茄汁比華人啦，後尾因為茄農嘅壓力下先令中間商正名叫ketchup。<br />\n但事件已經對當時有好大影響，咁小販為左取代原先茄汁嘅位置，就搵左芥末汁啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夢景完畢。"},{"pid":"9d0b4076e9c1944a313606dffd24221797716ced","tid":1285153,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"64a86498ac713ceab1e9fe53df67f85fe19cff61","tid":1285153,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff44570fb69696f572b07faaf11c36ba7e3309ba","tid":1285153,"uid":99568,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:55:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KwWde8DSj_E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKwWde8DSj_E&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=a1b3b5d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KwWde8DSj_E</a><br />\n蓋清 嘅飲食口味 同達哥好似"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:07:30.000Z","msg":"蓋清真兄弟嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:25:06.000Z","msg":"可能係本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c46e2fdb07e804375f3f0085d4e0c3a9777d75e","tid":1285153,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64a86498ac713ceab1e9fe53df67f85fe19cff61","tid":1285153,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff44570fb69696f572b07faaf11c36ba7e3309ba","tid":1285153,"uid